        {
          "author": "tireddy2",
          "authorAssociation": "OWNER",
          "body": "> Scope question: This is currently defined for CBOR/CWT, but EAT also supports JSON/JWT. Are there use cases that require JSON?\r\n\r\nIt may be useful for ACME which uses JSON, I will raise a separate PR.",
          "createdAt": "2026-06-05T07:35:40Z",
