          "comments": [
            {
              "originalPosition": 34,
              "body": "I agree with Ionut. The word \u201cplatform\u201d, at least in Arm circles, tends to be associated with the lower layers of the TCB.\r\nPerhaps \"Attester\u2019s TCB\u201d _may_ be more generally applicable.",
              "createdAt": "2026-06-04T17:04:48Z",
